name: Japanese Print Bag
description: This is a very pretty handmade tote bag suitable for shopping or carrying books etc. It is made from a polyester/cotton mix fabric which is black with a gorgeous Japanese inspired print of fans and flowers, in different shades of purple, pink, cream and green, with gold details. It is lined with black polyester and has a fully lined pocket on the outside. It measures 14.5 inches wide, 16 inches long, and the handles are 32.5 inches long. The front pocket is 6.5 inches by 5 inches. This bag is very eyecatching and unusual, and would certainly brighten up a trip to the supermarket! This item is new and has been handmade by me. I have a small business making and selling bags, jewellery and other accessories, but I have a back log of unsold stock which is why I am listing things on ebay. All my items come from a smoke and pet free home. Thanks for looking and please take a look at my other items.

name: Macaroon Bracelet
description: This macaroon bracelet has been handmade using polymer clay. Tiny macaroons in different shades of blue, green, pink, red, brown, purple, yellow and orange hang from a chunky silver plated chain. Each one has been modelled by hand and baked before being glazed with a shiny varnish. Some of the macaroons have a slight shimmer effect for added cuteness. The bracelet measures from end to end and fastens with a lobster clasp. There is an extender chain so the bracelet can be made slightly larger if needed. This bracelet really is the height of cuteness, perfect for any macaroon lover and bound to catch people's eye.

name: World Traveller Wool Cape
description: This beautiful cape has been made from a vintage striped wool fabric and is one of a kind.
